ro" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Intro</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#prerequisites" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Prerequisites</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#getting-started" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Getting Started</a><ul><li><a href="sign-windows#a-convert-your-cer-to-pfx" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">A. Convert your <code>.cer</code> to <code>.pfx</code></a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#b-import-your-pfx-file-into-the-keystore" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">B. Import your <code>.pfx</code> file into the keystore.</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#c-prepare-variables" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">C. Prepare Variables</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="sign-windows#prepare-tauriconfjson-file" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Prepare <code>tauri.conf.json</code> file</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#bonus-sign-your-application-with-github-actions" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">BONUS: Sign your application with GitHub Actions.</a><ul><li><a href="sign-windows#github-secrets" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">GitHub Secrets</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#workflow-modifications" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">Workflow Modifications</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div></div></main></div></div><footer class="footer footer--dark"><div class="container container-fluid"><div class="row footer__links"><div class="col footer__col"><div class="footer__title">Repositories</div><ul class="footer__items clean-list"><li class="footer__item"><a href="https://github.com/tauri-apps/tauri" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="footer__link-item">Tauri<svg width="13.5" height="13.5" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="iconExternalLink_nPIU"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21 13v10h-21v-19h12v2h-10v15h17v-8h2zm3-12h-10.988l4.035 4-6.977 7.07 2.828 2.828 6.977-7.07 4.125 4.172v-11z"></path></svg></a